Heal me, <HI>O LORD,</HI> &amp; I &s;hall be healed: &s;ave me, and I &s;hall be &s;aved.</Q>
<Q><BIBL>Exod. 15.26.</BIBL>
I am the <HI>LORD</HI> that healeth thee.</Q>
